
.. only:: html

    .. hint::

        This Python application can generate a system executable with Bash completions support for itself and for all applications it manages. See ``app.py gen_sys_exec_self`` and ``app.py gen_sys_exec_all``.

.. only:: man

    Hint
    ====

    This Python application can generate a system executable with Bash completions support for itself and for all applications it manages. See ``app.py gen_sys_exec_self`` and ``app.py gen_sys_exec_all``.
